## Credit System

Analyses beyond plan limits are purchased as one-off credits:

| Plan       | Included  | Extra credit price |
|------------|-----------|--------------------|
| Free       | 1/month   | N/A (upgrade)      |
| Starter    | 5/month   | €9 each            |
| Growth     | 20/month  | €7 each            |
| Enterprise | Unlimited | N/A                |

Credits do not expire. Unused monthly included credits reset.
Purchased extra credits carry over indefinitely.

---

## What Counts as One Analysis

One analysis = one AWS account scanned against one or more target clouds.

- Re-running the same account = a new analysis (credits consumed)
- Viewing a past report = free, no credit consumed
- Changing only the target cloud on an existing scan = new analysis
  (data is re-scored, not re-discovered, but counts as a new run)

Rationale: each run reflects a point-in-time snapshot of the account.
As infrastructure changes, the analysis becomes stale. Running again is
the core recurring action — it should cost credits to create that habit.

---

## Annual vs Monthly

Annual plans offered at ~20% discount.
Annual billed upfront — creates committed ARR, reduces churn.
Monthly available for Starter and Growth (no discount).
Enterprise is always annual contract.

