## Competitive Positioning

| Tool                | What it does                                         | Price                    |
|---------------------|------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------|
| AWS Migration Hub   | AWS-to-AWS only, no EU sovereign cloud support       | Free (AWS-locked)        |
| CloudQuery          | Raw data extraction, no compatibility analysis       | Open source / enterprise |
| Steampipe           | SQL queries on cloud data, no scoring                | Open source / enterprise |
| Manual consultant   | Expensive, slow, non-reproducible                    | €5k–€50k/engagement      |
| **Noblinks Lens**   | **Deterministic EU sovereignty analysis in minutes** | **€49–custom**           |

The closest competitor is a consultant engagement costing €5k–€50k
and taking 4–8 weeks. Lens does it in 60 seconds for €49/month.
That is the comparison to lead with in sales.

